data.description: Move in ready and one level living in this beautiful 3 br/2 ba rancher located in the desireable and peaceful River Vista Subdivision. This home features a large family/living room with kitchen/dining combo, split bedrooms, laundry room and 2 car attached garage. Master bedroom with whirlpool tub, walk in shower and huge his and her closets.  This home sits slightly back from the street providing for additional privacy , peace and quiet. Covered front and back porches to sit and reflect and enjoy the outdoor living.. A completely fenced in back yard provides plenty of room and safety for children and  pets. Centrally located in Sevier county.   Convenient to I-40, Douglas Lake, Sevierille, Pigeon Forge,  and the Smoky Mountains.
